title: Definitions
context: PART V. OFFICE OF AEROSPACE DEVELOPMENT Note Part heading amended by L 2007, c 149, §2(1). A. General Provisions Note Subpart heading designation added by L 2012, c 169, §3. §201-71 Definitions. As used in this part: &ldquo;Board&rdquo; means the board of directors of the Pacific international space center for exploration systems. &ldquo;Director&rdquo; means the director of the office of aerospace development. &ldquo;Office&rdquo; means the office of aerospace development. &ldquo;Space center&rdquo; means the Pacific international space center for exploration systems. [L 1988, c 355, pt of §2; am L 2007, c 149, §2(2); am L 2012, c 169, §4]
